Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:51.69,Article,,0000,0000,0000,,Customer service in Japanese style inns\Nis inevitably focused on emphasizing the individual\Ntraits of the proprietress and employees
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 23\NCompensation for the Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You awake, Minchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:12.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think this place \Nwill be shut down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:17.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose there's anything \Nwe can do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:24.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She's up before me, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This place really is going \Nto be shut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.98,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you go and persuade \Nthe Madam Manager, Mr. Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:36.21,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'd listen to {\i1}you{\i0}, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.68,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Time sure flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:41.97,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this inn when \NI was about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.32,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I've known the Madam \NManager ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.60,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,She's made such a big decision this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.02,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing anyone can say \Nwill change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.57,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Nako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.32,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Nako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.03,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.10,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,You should already know this, \Nbut the morning greeting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of the most basic \Nrequirements for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.04,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:27.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we'll need \Nthat much white radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The only customers are in the Wave Room,\N which Nakochi is in charge of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be fine, Minchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can peel white radish like a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You can work anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:45.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you and Tohru are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotary slicing, not peeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:48.82,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.72,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on becoming a fine chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You have a goal set in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.52,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.83,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam Manager is \Ncalling for you, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.69,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.69,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious ginger tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:25.13,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Mom said something\Nlike that out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's the inn's financial state...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.52,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Enishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:30.08,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.24,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the catchphrase
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been using since college?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.75,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,"Time is money," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.74,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps it was "killing \Ntwo birds with one stone."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.59,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe, "always have a smile on"—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.76,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,"Never give up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.85,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get back the money that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were stupidly tricked out of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.45,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.48,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you put it a bit nicer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.79,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan on doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.83,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in, Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.24,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:20.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I will be heading to \NTokyo now, Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.54,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.71,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, great timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.37,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Take this girl along as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.18,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.97,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Meet up with your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and discuss future plans with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.81,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,But I need you back here \Nin two days, no later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.08,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,The busiest time for the inns\Nin Yunosagi is during
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Bonbori Festival, \Nwhich starts next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.60,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready quickly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.79,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.96,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear you're heading to Tokyo, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam Manager told me \Nto go and meet with my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What are your future plans, Jiromaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.50,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she said she'll let \Nme off the hook here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you'll be a free man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.52,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm the only \None happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And where do you plan \Non living from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:18.89,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:19.94,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.69,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I going to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.39,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.98,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:45.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.89,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.26,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Your crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.85,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.39,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.06,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You need to meet up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.10,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You cheered me up a bit, Nakochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.07,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I have \Nsomething from Minchi—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.20,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking you so long?! \NI'm leaving you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.69,Default,Jirio,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.81,Default,Jirio,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana's got a lot on her \Nhands, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.05,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you worry about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before you worry about others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.55,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.25,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where's the young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.47,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.74,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's off crying somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since he's all alone, after \Nhaving just been married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.51,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.93,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Beanman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:43.18,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takky went off to Tokyo, Beanman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.81,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd do \Neverything by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:49.09,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I should go after her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.49,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.58,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not in my character,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but allow me to speak my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:08:00.00,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,I think Takako considers this Tokyo trip
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her first task as the next young \NMadam Manager of Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.50,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The next young Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.05,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.30,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,It's also a man's duty to sit and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:16.95,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.56,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it found itself a \Ncompanion for today's trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.01,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to be \Nbabysitting a high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give old aunties trouble—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.82,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,"Old aunties"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:51.51,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean my mother's brother's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:54.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Which makes you... my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.98,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,So that makes you my niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Technically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.85,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "big sis," then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Balut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.35,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.29,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.42,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that you, Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.61,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:37.12,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:40.08,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're as well-mannered as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.22,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,In case you're wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:48.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,it's no longer the mother's \Nproblem when a daughter this age
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gets dumped or gets knocked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:54.49,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's no way a healthy \Nboy can stand being so far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.33,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,you have no reason to feel \Nawkward just because
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you had a long distance \Nrelationship with
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my daughter and then \Nproceeded to dump her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.50,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ohana doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:09.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think a woman \Nwho got dumped is doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.59,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't dump her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.88,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The food cart lady sure is \Ntaking her time in getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've got lunches that Minchi made for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.58,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say so earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.14,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,This looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.74,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Madam Manager's \None and only grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:40.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.58,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hoping to become \Nthe Madam Manager someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:47.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've never wanted to\Nbecome the Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.33,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:51.97,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It {\i1}is{\i0} good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.42,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to eat? \NIt's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.54,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The spinach has been \Nseasoned very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:12.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi tasted these before she \Nserved them to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.80,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Of course she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:18.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Of course she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:23.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She also peeled the skin off \Nof these potatoes so neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:30.11,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:36.17,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose you two would \Nhave been doing well together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I hadn't decided to flee that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.26,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can say, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.69,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not uncommon for children
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have to move because \Nof their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.81,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,And since she is being fed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe there was no other option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.52,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,That's... how Ohana probably felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:58.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So you do know a lot about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.40,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.69,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me more about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:05.19,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even seen her \Nworking at the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.21,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.34,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Follow me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:18.59,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are your plans now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm going to\Ntalk with my mom about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.15,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come to Kissuiso in the hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of living with your mother again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:31.71,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you're young, so \Nyou've got it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.74,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a boyfriend waiting \Nfor you back in Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:43.06,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You don't need \Nto be such a crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.43,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something to make you cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.20,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.56,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come to Kissuiso \Nbecause of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.67,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,and even though you're young,\Nyou've got it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.27,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you don't have \Na boyfriend in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.44,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:02.29,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, may I have a can of beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.79,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.25,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,And what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.85,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,And a cola, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and some black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:13.32,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:22.11,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.76,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this distance\Nbetween an aunt and her niece?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.48,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. My aunt was absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't come to Kissuiso\Nbecause there was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}something I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not struggling that \Nhard in life, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:52.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yeah, Ko is in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:56.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's not my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:01.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's just a crush of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:09.30,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to \Nfind that producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.42,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I actually have some information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,given to me by my sister-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, sister-in-law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.21,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. The person you're \Ngoing to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.38,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.80,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,She is {\i1}so{\i0} reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important matter \Nregarding the Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't just leave everything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to my mom and you, aun- big sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.81,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for you to \Ntake off from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.77,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I had a coworker cover my shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:43.70,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for you as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've already done everything \NI need to for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all I really "did" \Nwas stand someone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.41,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:16.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.10,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing better in the world \Nthan a cunning older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.01,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Watch... helevator...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.29,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,He's a fast one, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.16,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.75,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he's still on this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.73,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Keep running and I'll tell \Neveryone what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:07.43,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:34.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My new auntie, I mean, big sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}seems to be pretty capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.45,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What, you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.47,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.46,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.46,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing this desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Sunday, there's \Nno one in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.21,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine with coffee, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.67,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.58,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't drink coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.02,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can have green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:24.95,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.03,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I love green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:30.92,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing you have the same \Ntastes as an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:43.35,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:46.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to watch porn with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.04,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.59,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.67,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.06,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that \Nunattractive of a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.86,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.92,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the most beautiful \Nof all my friends' mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:03.30,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.52,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:18.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The Kissuiso. Where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:21.36,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's where Ohana works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.50,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.62,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.06,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There was some talk about a film
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Kissuiso as its setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.97,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It was called off in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.97,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but this is footage \Nfrom the camera tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the producer of the film
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wanted nothing more to do with it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after the plans were called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.31,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So he sent it to me asking if I'd like\Nto use it in my next article.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off even more
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he thought he'd be \Nforgiven after doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.16,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my first time watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:08.42,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.48,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is sweetfish, and this is mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.46,Default,[x]Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Two additional servings of \Nsashimi in the Wisteria Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.95,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind answering a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:23.71,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. Act naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:24.85,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.47,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Do you find work difficult, Miss Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I love festing it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:34.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,err, working my hardest \Nwith everyone, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:37.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That was Nakochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Mind telling us a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.95,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You came from Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your own to be trained \Nas a waitress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about "training"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.11,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,And you're only in high \Nschool. Isn't it difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:53.52,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your friends \Nand family in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:56.00,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you leave your\Nboyfriend behind as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't leave him behind.\NKo's also working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a matter of leaving \Nbehind or being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.36,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for these sudden questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you mind telling us \Nwhat your job is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.05,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Majima Tomoe, and I \Nwork as the head waitress here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:18.33,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Tomoe, you're not acting like usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.33,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that seems like a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.15,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,About 6 years, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.23,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have some coffee, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.23,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,And your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you couldn't drink coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.78,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty...three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.58,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, twenty-three...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.08,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:55.22,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I had some was with\Nyour daughter- with Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.11,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.67,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,The kind they served at the restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was bland and not very good,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:05.73,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,but I kind of wanted to keep \Nthat taste in my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.62,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.74,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had coffee since.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:14.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How's it taste after not \Nhaving it for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.48,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to excuse myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.35,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.22,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:29.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so honored to have our inn \Nstage Mr. Matsuura's next film.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:48.00,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Ms. Matsumae.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.80,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I had almost given up on Ohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:56.50,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, you're nothing \Nlike a bland coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:42.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too swift on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:46.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But this is obvious enough \Nfor even me to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:47.40,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 24\NSui Shijima, the Final Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say all these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
